1. *Kolica* su mi ostala u prodavnici. (The *shopping cart* stayed in the store.)
2. *Kolica* su veoma korisna kada idete u kupovinu. (The *shopping cart* is very useful when you go shopping.)
3. Kada sam bila mala, vozila sam se u *kolicima*. (When I was little, I used to ride in a *baby carriage*.)
4. Hranila sam bebu dok je bila u *kolicima*. (I fed the baby while she was in the *stroller*.)
5. Juče sam sređivala sobu i našla sam stare dečje *kolice*. (Yesterday, I was cleaning the room and found old children's *pram*.)
6. Danas mi je veoma teško da guram *kolica* sa bebom zbog snega. (Today, it's very hard for me to push the *stroller* with the baby because of the snow.)
7. Molim vas, vratite mi moja *kolica* za kupovinu. (Please, return my *shopping cart* to me.)
8. Ne znam kako ću da prenesem sve ove stvari bez *kolica*. (I don't know how I'm going to carry all these things without a *cart*.)